d17dba67-413a-4029-8de9-b04ae811e982.title: Commander Montai
d17dba67-413a-4029-8de9-b04ae811e982.text:
I can't talk now. Can't you see we're trying to win a
battle here? If we can't hold back Khazard's men we're
all doomed.

c53d84d9-6426-4c10-b9cb-a9d961d67ad3.title: Commander Montai
c53d84d9-6426-4c10-b9cb-a9d961d67ad3.text: Hello traveller, are you here to help or just to watch?

e5725dc2-e242-4256-b54b-bf199f877caa.title: <player>
e5725dc2-e242-4256-b54b-bf199f877caa.text:
I've been sent by King Bolren to retrieve the orb of
protection.

574967cc-fd4f-4114-ad9a-bbf4d16374de.title: Commander Montai
574967cc-fd4f-4114-ad9a-bbf4d16374de.text: Excellent we need all the help we can get.

01030b47-2ed7-4ca6-849b-202aa8d6384e.title: Commander Montai
01030b47-2ed7-4ca6-849b-202aa8d6384e.text:
I'm commander Montai. The orb is in the Khazard
stronghold to the north, but until we weaken their
defences we can't get close.

c0aba89d-fb02-4126-8283-1d1f1bd5c931.title: Commander Montai
c0aba89d-fb02-4126-8283-1d1f1bd5c931.text:
Firstly we need to strengthen our own defences. We
desperately need wood to make more battlements, once
the battlements are gone it's all over. Six loads of
normal logs should do it.

options.text: Sorry, I no longer want to be involved.

06a6d585-6dff-456d-ad5d-5a0e7a61484c.title: <player>
06a6d585-6dff-456d-ad5d-5a0e7a61484c.text: Sorry I no longer want to be involved.

e3d9c2f3-897f-4e73-aa5d-d5959c66ecf7.title: Commander Montai
e3d9c2f3-897f-4e73-aa5d-d5959c66ecf7.text: That's a shame, we could have done with your help.

d105dd4f-ad2f-4433-87d4-620783bd0756.title: Commander Montai
d105dd4f-ad2f-4433-87d4-620783bd0756.text:
Please be as quick as you can, I don't know how much
longer we can hold out.

bd9fd052-1fb1-4d2a-9093-321f426910b4.title: Commander Montai
bd9fd052-1fb1-4d2a-9093-321f426910b4.text:
Hello again, we're still desperate for wood soldier. We
need six loads of normal logs.

bf8c3d1a-e2fe-48e4-b15a-3bd4b5af9590.title: <player>
bf8c3d1a-e2fe-48e4-b15a-3bd4b5af9590.text: I'll see what I can do.

ec4cbcee-875c-4299-b8b4-f7e5b12c973a.title: Commander Montai
ec4cbcee-875c-4299-b8b4-f7e5b12c973a.text: Hello again, we're still desperate for wood soldier.

0c1648f1-9f6f-441e-aea2-f01f3ee5c17b.title: <player>
0c1648f1-9f6f-441e-aea2-f01f3ee5c17b.text:
I have some here.
(You give six loads of logs to the commander.)

216a9dda-00b0-4d1b-90f2-015db8be12ee.title: Commander Montai
216a9dda-00b0-4d1b-90f2-015db8be12ee.text:
That's excellent, now we can make more defensive
battlements.  Give me a moment to organise the troops
and then come speak to me. I'll inform you of our next
phase of attack.

5efd0cde-7d82-4dd1-b83b-cd55e7c18c08.text: You need 6 normal logs in your inventory.

4808a4e2-42aa-4844-a68f-5a7cba52d364.title: Note
4808a4e2-42aa-4844-a68f-5a7cba52d364.text:
logs given, now to talk about
the next step

765ba287-77e0-48a8-bb48-70c4a4356eaa.title: Commander Montai
765ba287-77e0-48a8-bb48-70c4a4356eaa.text:
We're hanging in there soldier. For the next phase of
our attack we need to breach their stronghold.

ba3aa032-25ce-4144-888e-79c41c01b244.title: Commander Montai
ba3aa032-25ce-4144-888e-79c41c01b244.text:
The ballista can break through the stronghold wall, and
then we can advance and seize back the orb.

2eb81bc2-2c40-4bcb-a05c-9083e1a2c2a7.title: Commander Montai
2eb81bc2-2c40-4bcb-a05c-9083e1a2c2a7.text:
From this distance we can't get an accurate enough
shot.  We need the correct coordinates of the
stronghold for a direct hit.  I've sent out three tracker
gnomes to gather them.

3f874441-778f-47ba-b28b-b0b84e2d0e62.title: Commander Montai
3f874441-778f-47ba-b28b-b0b84e2d0e62.text:
I'm afraid not, and we're running out of time. I need
you to go into the heart of the battlefield, find the
trackers, and bring back the coordinates.

9847f1ea-9039-406e-9a1f-1eeb23d147cf.title: Commander Montai
9847f1ea-9039-406e-9a1f-1eeb23d147cf.text: Do you think you can do it?

options.text: No, I've had enough of your battle.

bd4d157a-3eb9-409d-ad85-f8188e90daf3.title: <player>
bd4d157a-3eb9-409d-ad85-f8188e90daf3.text: No, I've had enough of your battle.

436140aa-5fff-409c-a5bd-fa26e3978de9.title: Commander Montai
436140aa-5fff-409c-a5bd-fa26e3978de9.text: I understand, this isn't your fight.

83b30b5b-ddbf-4a11-9f6e-78fa5297292d.title: Commander Montai
83b30b5b-ddbf-4a11-9f6e-78fa5297292d.text: Thank you, you're braver than most.

2997f4b6-7b8a-4b8c-97a1-d58485b94b5c.title: Commander Montai
2997f4b6-7b8a-4b8c-97a1-d58485b94b5c.text:
I don't know how long I will be able to hold out. Once
you have the coordinates come back and fire the ballista
right into those monsters.

4f9a9159-504b-42a5-9b2b-f8947635f660.title: Commander Montai
4f9a9159-504b-42a5-9b2b-f8947635f660.text:
If you can retrieve the orb and bring safety back to
my people, none of the blood spilled on this field will be
in vain.

3165f11c-e1af-42e8-9478-3b86e33b97b0.title: Commander Montai
3165f11c-e1af-42e8-9478-3b86e33b97b0.text:
Hello warrior. We need the coordinates for a direct hit
from the ballista. Once you have a direct hit you will be
able to enter the stronghold and retrieve the orb.

ce14d9cb-57b6-4756-858d-02516c310ca3.title: Commander Montai
ce14d9cb-57b6-4756-858d-02516c310ca3.text:
I saw, that was a beautiful sight. The Khazard troops
didn't know what hit them.

97e71bb2-289d-4cc7-8e88-991374c4d93f.title: Commander Montai
97e71bb2-289d-4cc7-8e88-991374c4d93f.text:
Now is the time to retrieve the orb. It's all in your
hands. I'll be praying for you.

b16a55c5-2b13-4e6f-8551-d7ae41280590.title: <player>
b16a55c5-2b13-4e6f-8551-d7ae41280590.text: I have the orb of protection.

29fedd76-4f53-4b4d-bbcd-7930de4efe7c.title: Commander Montai
29fedd76-4f53-4b4d-bbcd-7930de4efe7c.text: Incredible, for a human you really are something.

ae8d8c7d-00d1-4d9f-9bac-413ad27cffd0.title: Commander Montai
ae8d8c7d-00d1-4d9f-9bac-413ad27cffd0.text:
I'll stay here with my troops and try and hold
Khazard's men back. You return the orb to the gnome
village. Go as quick as you can, the village is still
unprotected.

800d9cf6-a0fc-495e-8272-1cb8b2796de1.title: Commander Montai
800d9cf6-a0fc-495e-8272-1cb8b2796de1.text:
I'm ok, this battle is going to take longer to win than I
expected. The Khazard troops won't give up even
without the orb.
